primary.context: Customer wants to settle their maintenance fee balance
primary.detail: Agent verified the account and sent a payment link via email and text.

steps: Customer requested to pay maintenance fees.
Agent initiated account lookup and verification.
Customer provided name and state of residence.
Agent confirmed contact details on file.
Agent sent payment link via text and email.

clarifications.note: Agent requested spelling after initial name miss

actions.detail: Verified name and state of residence
Sent maintenance fee link to email and SMS

insights.summary: The customer successfully requested and received a payment link for maintenance fees after a standard verification process.
